{"title":"Eclipse配置Go语言环境，并运行第一个Go项目","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.053Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/Eclipse配置Go语言环境，并运行第一个Go项目","updated":"2023-07-28T08:53:44.006Z","content":"<h1 id=\"一、首先准备工作\">一、首先准备工作<a title=\"#一、首先准备工作\" href=\"#一、首先准备工作\"></a></h1>\n<p>1、准备go语言的运行环境，可以参考<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/109726745\" target=\"_blank\">这个https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/109726745</a><br>\n2、准备eclipse的Go语言插件<br>\nHelp-&gt;Install New Software</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201120223110749.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n然后在“Work with”内输入：<a href=\"http://goclipse.github.io/releases/%EF%BC%8C%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%8C%89%E5%9B%9E%E8%BD%A6%E9%94%AE%E5%8D%B3%E5%8F%AF%EF%BC%9B%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E4%BD%A0%E5%95%A5%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%82%EF%BC%8C%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E5%B0%8F%E7%99%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%8B%BE%E9%80%89%E5%89%8D%E9%9D%A23%E4%B8%AA%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E7%82%B9next%E3%80%82\" target=\"_blank\">http://goclipse.github.io/releases/，直接按回车键即可；如果你啥也不懂，真的是小白，可以勾选前面3个选项，一直点next。</a><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201120223255513.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>在Preference—&gt;Go，设置go环境的位置，到bin目录的<strong>上一层</strong>即可<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201120224012929.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>然后下载go语言在eclipse里面运行的3个软件<br>\ngocode.exe<br>\ngodef.exe<br>\nguru.exe<br>\n这三个软件如果直接点download，会因为不能连接外网而下载不了<br>\n建议先从github上下好源码，在本地编译出来，然后添加进eclipse<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201120223532383.png#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\nPreference—&gt;Go—&gt;Tools,按下图放置，顺便把gofmt文件的位置也丢上去。<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/202011202239477.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"二、运行项目\">二、运行项目<a title=\"#二、运行项目\" href=\"#二、运行项目\"></a></h1>\n<p>新建Go project<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201120224323345.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201120224338965.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n在src下面新建一个main文件夹，再新建一个Go File，输入如下代码，右击-&gt;Run As-&gt;Go Application，<br>\n（注意：1、你的文件目录结构必须跟我这个一样，文件夹的图标样式也必须一样，否则可能报错<br>\n2、fmt.Println注意“P”大写，小写会报错）<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201120224400935.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n运行成功<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201120224535113.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"ERROR_ ‘_usr_sbin_iptables-restore -w -n‘ failed_ iptables-restore v1.8.2 (nf_tables)","link":"2023/07/28/ERROR_ ‘_usr_sbin_iptables-restore -w -n‘ failed_ iptables-restore v1.8.2 (nf_tables)"},"next":{"title":"docker常用命令","link":"2023/07/28/docker常用命令"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/Eclipse配置Go语言环境，并运行第一个Go项目/","toc":[{"id":"一、首先准备工作","title":"一、首先准备工作","index":"1"},{"id":"二、运行项目","title":"二、运行项目","index":"2"}],"reading_time":"543 字约 4 分钟"}